1
00:00:15,738 --> 00:00:17,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Excuse me.</font>

2
00:00:18,438 --> 00:00:21,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh, I was thinking
about having some coffee.</font>

3
00:00:23,371 --> 00:00:24,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who else wants some?</font>

4
00:00:34,472 --> 00:00:36,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK. Got it.</font>

5
00:00:38,238 --> 00:00:39,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah. I forgot.</font>

6
00:00:40,472 --> 00:00:43,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Roast pork. I brought a whole one.</font>

7
00:00:43,438 --> 00:00:44,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wow!</font>

8
00:00:45,138 --> 00:00:46,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll put it in your fridge.</font>

9
00:00:50,438 --> 00:00:51,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">RULES</font>

10
00:00:58,138 --> 00:00:59,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Your room is really clean.</font>

11
00:00:59,205 --> 00:01:02,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can change in here,
but you sleep on the sofa.</font>

12
00:01:03,205 --> 00:01:04,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can sleep anywhere.</font>

13
00:01:04,371 --> 00:01:07,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">All the other stuff is on that paper.</font>

14
00:01:07,872 --> 00:01:09,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, you mean those rules on the fridge?</font>

15
00:01:10,039 --> 00:01:11,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

16
00:01:12,171 --> 00:01:14,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, I've got work now.</font>

17
00:01:15,438 --> 00:01:17,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't pull any funny business.</font>

18
00:01:17,138 --> 00:01:19,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-How boyfriend-like.
-Shut up.</font>

19
00:01:19,338 --> 00:01:20,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks for letting me stay.</font>

20
00:01:23,405 --> 00:01:24,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's with you?</font>

21
00:01:54,939 --> 00:01:56,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, you're back.</font>

22
00:01:58,405 --> 00:02:00,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think Nao's still sleeping.</font>

23
00:02:00,705 --> 00:02:01,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

24
00:02:03,605 --> 00:02:06,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No need to rush home.
I'm not going to do anything to her.</font>

25
00:02:06,338 --> 00:02:07,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who said I was rushing?</font>

26
00:02:09,205 --> 00:02:11,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Evening Star special pork roast fried rice</i></font>

27
00:02:11,371 --> 00:02:12,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">with wonton soup.</font>

28
00:02:12,305 --> 00:02:13,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Wow!
-Nice!</font>

29
00:02:14,005 --> 00:02:15,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks.</font>

30
00:02:15,105 --> 00:02:16,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Thank you.
-My pleasure.</font>

31
00:02:28,271 --> 00:02:29,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is better than I can do.</font>

32
00:02:29,672 --> 00:02:31,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll cook for you guys
while I'm staying here.</font>

33
00:02:31,839 --> 00:02:32,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Seriously?
-What?</font>

34
00:02:34,405 --> 00:02:36,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't you dare tell my dad
where I'm at, Nao.</font>

35
00:02:37,039 --> 00:02:38,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I won't.</font>

36
00:02:39,338 --> 00:02:40,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is delicious, Issei.</font>

37
00:02:40,905 --> 00:02:42,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Can I get seconds?
-Yeah.</font>

38
00:02:42,872 --> 00:02:44,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks.</font>

39
00:02:46,371 --> 00:02:47,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're used to this, aren't you?</font>

40
00:02:47,738 --> 00:02:49,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course I am.</font>

41
00:02:50,939 --> 00:02:52,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Next one.
-Here.</font>

42
00:02:56,271 --> 00:02:58,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Here.
-I'm not ready yet.</font>

43
00:02:58,305 --> 00:02:59,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

44
00:02:59,271 --> 00:03:00,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Rinse it.
-Look what you did!</font>

45
00:03:00,438 --> 00:03:01,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's onion still--</font>

46
00:03:09,572 --> 00:03:11,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can take a bath now.</font>

47
00:03:12,271 --> 00:03:14,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Get to bed.
-Huh?</font>

48
00:03:14,205 --> 00:03:15,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's late.</font>

49
00:03:16,171 --> 00:03:17,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, it's not.</font>

50
00:03:17,572 --> 00:03:18,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Come on.
-I'm not sleepy either.</font>

51
00:03:18,872 --> 00:03:19,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I said go to bed.</font>

52
00:03:19,905 --> 00:03:22,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Why? It's not late.
-That doesn't matter. Get to bed.</font>

53
00:03:22,772 --> 00:03:24,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not sleepy at all. What're you doing?</font>

54
00:03:24,939 --> 00:03:26,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Do as I say. Get to bed.
-No way! I'm not going to bed!</font>

55
00:03:27,039 --> 00:03:28,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! What're you doing?</font>

56
00:03:32,538 --> 00:03:34,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can take a bath first.</font>

57
00:03:35,672 --> 00:03:38,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, OK. Thanks.</font>

58
00:04:19,105 --> 00:04:20,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Time to get up!</i></font>

59
00:04:28,472 --> 00:04:30,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is <i>way better than I can do.</i></font>

60
00:04:31,205 --> 00:04:32,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Bon appétit.</font>

61
00:04:32,872 --> 00:04:35,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Bon appétit.
-Bon appétit.</font>

62
00:04:42,271 --> 00:04:43,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's hot!</font>

63
00:04:47,738 --> 00:04:49,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is great, Issei!</font>

64
00:04:51,505 --> 00:04:53,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Hey, Issei.
-Huh?</font>

65
00:04:53,638 --> 00:04:56,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You've got bad bed head.
-I do?</font>

66
00:04:59,672 --> 00:05:00,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Where's it funny?
-Right here.</font>

67
00:05:01,805 --> 00:05:03,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Turn that way.
-Where is it?</font>

68
00:05:03,305 --> 00:05:05,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I said turn that way.
-Ow! That hurt!</font>

69
00:05:05,839 --> 00:05:07,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I haven't even touched it.
-I'm done.</font>

70
00:05:08,171 --> 00:05:11,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? You're done eating already?
You usually have three bowls of rice.</font>

71
00:05:11,638 --> 00:05:12,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's time to go.</font>

72
00:05:13,039 --> 00:05:13,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Sorry.
-It's OK.</font>

73
00:05:14,039 --> 00:05:17,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! Oh, no! Oh, no! Oh, no!</font>

74
00:05:20,005 --> 00:05:21,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Forget about eating. Get going!</font>

75
00:05:21,805 --> 00:05:25,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hurry up! You'll be late!</font>

76
00:05:26,005 --> 00:05:27,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Leave some for me.
-OK.</font>

77
00:05:27,705 --> 00:05:28,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry, Issei.</font>

78
00:05:28,738 --> 00:05:30,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It's OK.
-See you later.</font>

79
00:05:32,138 --> 00:05:34,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, can you lend me your house key?</font>

80
00:05:34,939 --> 00:05:36,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-My key?
-Yeah.</font>

81
00:05:36,538 --> 00:05:39,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's not safe to go out
without locking the door.</font>

82
00:05:39,572 --> 00:05:41,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah. You're right.</font>

83
00:05:59,605 --> 00:06:00,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

84
00:06:02,872 --> 00:06:03,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks.</font>

85
00:06:04,905 --> 00:06:06,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, wait for me!</font>

86
00:06:06,305 --> 00:06:08,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Bye! See you later.
-Bye.</font>

87
00:06:15,271 --> 00:06:17,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait up for me, Uehara!</font>

88
00:06:18,872 --> 00:06:19,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara!</font>

89
00:06:22,939 --> 00:06:24,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait for me, would you?</font>

90
00:06:32,138 --> 00:06:33,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yu!</font>

91
00:06:33,105 --> 00:06:34,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Aren't you going to talk to him?</font>

92
00:06:37,705 --> 00:06:39,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Isn't that why you came?</font>

93
00:06:41,638 --> 00:06:43,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's OK. I'll come back again later.</font>

94
00:06:47,605 --> 00:06:48,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really? Issei?</font>

95
00:06:48,972 --> 00:06:52,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah. He and his dad had an argument.</font>

96
00:06:52,338 --> 00:06:55,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I'm partly to blame for it.</font>

97
00:06:56,238 --> 00:07:01,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Two handsome guys... under one roof.</font>

98
00:07:02,005 --> 00:07:03,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina? Marina!</font>

99
00:07:04,472 --> 00:07:07,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh! I've got to go!
-Why? That's just the first bell.</font>

100
00:07:07,438 --> 00:07:10,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Haven't you heard?
There's a university student here today.</font>

101
00:07:10,939 --> 00:07:12,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Really?
-Yes! A student teacher!</font>

102
00:07:12,805 --> 00:07:14,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got to go check him out.</font>

103
00:07:16,738 --> 00:07:21,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Has she forgotten that I'm her boyfriend?</font>

104
00:07:22,805 --> 00:07:24,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wouldn't worry about it.</font>

105
00:07:27,672 --> 00:07:30,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm Senzaki Yu,
a senior from Joso University.</font>

106
00:07:30,705 --> 00:07:32,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll be your teacher
for the next two weeks.</font>

107
00:07:35,805 --> 00:07:36,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes! He's hot!</font>

108
00:07:41,605 --> 00:07:42,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Excuse me!</font>

109
00:07:44,538 --> 00:07:45,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, my girl!</font>

110
00:07:45,438 --> 00:07:48,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't talk like that to me!</font>

111
00:07:48,338 --> 00:07:49,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You are a teacher, after all.</font>

112
00:07:49,839 --> 00:07:51,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm so glad we could meet again, dear!</font>

113
00:07:51,672 --> 00:07:54,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I told you, quit talking like that!</font>

114
00:07:54,371 --> 00:07:57,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">To be honest,
I came here so I could see you.</font>

115
00:07:57,638 --> 00:07:58,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

116
00:07:58,538 --> 00:08:01,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't act so mean.
Let's try to get along, OK?</font>

117
00:08:01,505 --> 00:08:03,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>-Nao!
-Cut that out!</i></font>

118
00:08:04,972 --> 00:08:06,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

119
00:08:08,105 --> 00:08:09,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who's that?</font>

120
00:08:09,205 --> 00:08:10,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's the student teacher--</font>

121
00:08:10,472 --> 00:08:12,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know exactly who you are!</font>

122
00:08:12,505 --> 00:08:14,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're one of the top three
hottest boys in school.</font>

123
00:08:14,605 --> 00:08:18,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Top of the class! Sportsman!
An all-around awesome guy!</font>

124
00:08:18,638 --> 00:08:19,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Twinkle, twinkle!</font>

125
00:08:20,105 --> 00:08:23,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh, he's not <i>that great.
-Why are you all giggly?</i></font>

126
00:08:24,271 --> 00:08:25,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry.</font>

127
00:08:25,271 --> 00:08:28,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So it's true. You two really are a couple.</font>

128
00:08:29,105 --> 00:08:32,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Such a pity!
I was so glad that I could see Nao again.</font>

129
00:08:33,371 --> 00:08:36,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm Senzaki Yu. I'll be working here
for the next two weeks.</font>

130
00:08:38,005 --> 00:08:39,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK?</font>

131
00:08:45,472 --> 00:08:47,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the hell is up with that guy?</font>

132
00:08:48,472 --> 00:08:51,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He was in the same hospital as me.</font>

133
00:08:52,538 --> 00:08:56,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So that's why he said "again."
What an unfortunate coincidence.</font>

134
00:08:56,305 --> 00:08:58,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was shocked to see him too.</font>

135
00:08:58,672 --> 00:09:01,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You didn't let slip about us to him,
did you?</font>

136
00:09:01,638 --> 00:09:04,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Of course I didn't.</font>

137
00:09:04,939 --> 00:09:08,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know,
you've been acting strange lately.</font>

138
00:09:08,638 --> 00:09:09,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're angry all the time.</font>

139
00:09:10,039 --> 00:09:13,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's because
you're always letting your guard down.</font>

140
00:09:14,305 --> 00:09:15,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Like this morning...</font>

141
00:09:16,105 --> 00:09:16,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This morning?</font>

142
00:09:20,738 --> 00:09:21,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Forget it.</font>

143
00:09:27,039 --> 00:09:29,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>-Miso ramen up!
-OK!</i></font>

144
00:09:29,105 --> 00:09:31,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here's your miso ramen. Enjoy!</font>

145
00:09:31,405 --> 00:09:34,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Excuse me!
-One moment, please.</font>

146
00:09:35,939 --> 00:09:38,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Damn him!
Right when we're busy, too.</font>

147
00:09:43,238 --> 00:09:47,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry, Nao. You have to work double hard
because of that stupid son of mine.</font>

148
00:09:49,505 --> 00:09:54,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm, sir. About those bowls...</font>

149
00:09:55,171 --> 00:09:58,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You see, it was me that broke them.</font>

150
00:09:59,105 --> 00:10:01,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I ran into Issei
while he was making the delivery.</font>

151
00:10:03,138 --> 00:10:05,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm very, very sorry.</font>

152
00:10:05,538 --> 00:10:07,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Forget about it, Nao.</font>

153
00:10:07,772 --> 00:10:11,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I already apologized to the customer.
It's taken care of.</font>

154
00:10:11,472 --> 00:10:13,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But, didn't you have
an argument about that?</font>

155
00:10:13,939 --> 00:10:16,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He told me
he wants to go learn somewhere else.</font>

156
00:10:17,338 --> 00:10:18,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

157
00:10:18,638 --> 00:10:21,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's gotten too big for his britches,
saying he's leaving.</font>

158
00:10:21,738 --> 00:10:25,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How can I let him work somewhere else
when he can't even do a proper job here?</font>

159
00:10:26,205 --> 00:10:30,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He told me so suddenly
that I lost my temper and...</font>

160
00:10:34,638 --> 00:10:36,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Good night.</font>

161
00:10:41,039 --> 00:10:42,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Issei?</font>

162
00:10:43,472 --> 00:10:46,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hi. What a coincidence.</font>

163
00:10:50,772 --> 00:10:51,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

164
00:10:51,672 --> 00:10:53,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Was it busy?</font>

165
00:10:55,138 --> 00:10:58,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Why? Does it bother you?
-No.</font>

166
00:10:59,105 --> 00:11:02,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really? Then I won't tell you.</font>

167
00:11:02,805 --> 00:11:05,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Now you're acting like Uehara.</font>

168
00:11:06,872 --> 00:11:08,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really? You're kidding!</font>

169
00:11:09,105 --> 00:11:12,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Like I said before, you'll become
more and more like each other.</font>

170
00:11:12,171 --> 00:11:13,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Like a married couple.</font>

171
00:11:14,105 --> 00:11:17,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, dear. Was I really being that mean?</font>

172
00:11:20,705 --> 00:11:23,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, so I guess</font>

173
00:11:23,205 --> 00:11:26,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">your mom was a lot like your dad too, huh?</font>

174
00:11:26,905 --> 00:11:28,271
