I'm sorry about the trouble.</font>

348
00:24:18,839 --> 00:24:20,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

349
00:24:20,072 --> 00:24:21,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

350
00:24:21,438 --> 00:24:23,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks for worrying about us.</font>

351
00:24:24,438 --> 00:24:25,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, I guess you're right.</font>

352
00:24:25,972 --> 00:24:29,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks to you, we know that this place is
in trouble without me.</font>

353
00:24:29,271 --> 00:24:30,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You're wrong.
-What?</font>

354
00:24:31,438 --> 00:24:33,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm never giving this shop
to an irresponsible ass like you.</font>

355
00:24:34,438 --> 00:24:35,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

356
00:24:36,238 --> 00:24:37,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Get some practice at a bigger shop.</font>

357
00:24:42,572 --> 00:24:46,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you don't,
I won't ever let you run the Evening Star.</font>

358
00:24:48,638 --> 00:24:49,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dad...</font>

359
00:24:50,138 --> 00:24:51,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Manager...</font>

360
00:24:51,438 --> 00:24:52,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's just like you said.</font>

361
00:24:52,738 --> 00:24:57,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's probably important for you
to work on your own for a while.</font>

362
00:24:59,438 --> 00:25:00,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Go ahead.</font>

363
00:25:04,338 --> 00:25:06,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why are you looking like that?</font>

364
00:25:06,572 --> 00:25:08,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Since you were little,
you were always by my side.</font>

365
00:25:08,839 --> 00:25:11,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You kept saying you'd take over after me.</font>

366
00:25:12,238 --> 00:25:15,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It was like your life was mine.</font>

367
00:25:16,371 --> 00:25:18,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But that's not right.</font>

368
00:25:20,438 --> 00:25:21,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry about what I did.</font>

369
00:25:32,905 --> 00:25:34,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm...</font>

370
00:25:35,405 --> 00:25:38,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry for saying what I did too,</font>

371
00:25:39,872 --> 00:25:41,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dad.</font>

372
00:25:52,805 --> 00:25:54,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Thanks for today.
-No problem.</font>

373
00:25:54,438 --> 00:25:56,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, here.</font>

374
00:25:57,572 --> 00:25:58,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll give it back to him.</font>

375
00:25:59,472 --> 00:26:01,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll get my bag tomorrow.</font>

376
00:26:01,738 --> 00:26:04,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK. See you later.</font>

377
00:26:08,572 --> 00:26:09,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao!</font>

378
00:26:15,438 --> 00:26:16,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm...</font>

379
00:26:18,572 --> 00:26:19,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

380
00:26:32,338 --> 00:26:33,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks.</font>

381
00:26:38,905 --> 00:26:40,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Bye.
-See you.</font>

382
00:26:58,705 --> 00:26:59,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hello?</font>

383
00:26:59,872 --> 00:27:03,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>How come you haven't answered your phone?</i></font>

384
00:27:03,171 --> 00:27:04,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's up?</font>

385
00:27:05,505 --> 00:27:08,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>-I made too much again.
-Oh, but I, uh...</i></font>

386
00:27:08,839 --> 00:27:10,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't you like fried chicken?</font>

387
00:27:11,505 --> 00:27:13,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yes, I do.
-Then here.</font>

388
00:27:14,039 --> 00:27:15,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It'll just go to waste.</font>

389
00:27:16,839 --> 00:27:18,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Actually, I made it for him.</font>

390
00:27:18,872 --> 00:27:21,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But he said
he doesn't need dinner tonight.</font>

391
00:27:28,305 --> 00:27:31,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, fine. Thanks.</font>

392
00:27:32,072 --> 00:27:33,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No problem.</font>

393
00:27:49,472 --> 00:27:51,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh. How's it going?</font>

394
00:27:57,238 --> 00:27:58,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao?</font>

395
00:28:01,738 --> 00:28:03,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you upset about something?</font>

396
00:28:06,672 --> 00:28:08,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't tell me
you got food poisoning again.</font>

397
00:28:09,572 --> 00:28:10,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course not!</font>

398
00:28:12,271 --> 00:28:13,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I see.</font>

399
00:28:21,039 --> 00:28:22,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

400
00:28:24,305 --> 00:28:26,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I think--
-Who was that girl just now?</font>

401
00:28:29,405 --> 00:28:32,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's a classmate from elementary school.</font>

402
00:28:36,138 --> 00:28:37,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's wrong?</font>

403
00:28:39,538 --> 00:28:43,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought you didn't like
receiving things from girls.</font>

404
00:28:44,005 --> 00:28:47,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But there's nothing I could do.
She came to the door.</font>

405
00:28:49,772 --> 00:28:52,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You took her to your work too, right?</font>

406
00:28:54,405 --> 00:28:55,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nanako told you?</font>

407
00:28:59,738 --> 00:29:01,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So it's true.</font>

408
00:29:03,438 --> 00:29:05,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've never even been there.</font>

409
00:29:07,371 --> 00:29:08,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't be stupid.</font>

410
00:29:10,438 --> 00:29:11,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This isn't stupid!</font>

411
00:29:15,171 --> 00:29:18,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know you'd never cheat on me.</font>

412
00:29:20,005 --> 00:29:24,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know that, but I still don't like it.</font>

413
00:29:24,572 --> 00:29:27,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't like feeling all jealous.</font>

414
00:29:27,271 --> 00:29:29,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't like being worried.</font>

415
00:29:33,039 --> 00:29:36,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want to believe that you'd never,
ever do such a thing,</font>

416
00:29:36,772 --> 00:29:37,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but...</font>

417
00:29:39,438 --> 00:29:43,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just can't be that confident.</font>

418
00:29:47,638 --> 00:29:48,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

419
00:29:57,839 --> 00:29:59,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Look at this.</font>

420
00:30:04,705 --> 00:30:07,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Break up with Uehara, or I'll tell
the school you're living together!</font>

421
00:30:07,572 --> 00:30:10,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It was taped to your locker at school.</font>

422
00:30:12,039 --> 00:30:13,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, my god.</font>

423
00:30:15,705 --> 00:30:16,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know...</font>

424
00:30:18,205 --> 00:30:19,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">when things like this happen...</font>

425
00:30:29,005 --> 00:30:30,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've been thinking about what to do.</font>

426
00:30:42,072 --> 00:30:43,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's move somewhere together.</font>

427
00:31:07,738 --> 00:31:08,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Together?</font>

428
00:31:09,972 --> 00:31:11,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

429
00:31:19,605 --> 00:31:21,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There you go crying again.</font>

430
00:31:30,072 --> 00:31:31,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't help it.</font>

431
00:31:52,972 --> 00:31:54,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Silly girl.</font>

432
00:32:05,271 --> 00:32:07,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Italian salami sure is good.</font>

433
00:32:07,405 --> 00:32:10,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! Darn you!</font>

434
00:32:15,872 --> 00:32:18,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know you want to move,</font>

435
00:32:18,271 --> 00:32:22,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but who would rent
to a couple of high school kids like us?</font>

436
00:32:24,772 --> 00:32:28,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Besides, I don't want to give in
to whoever is doing this.</font>

437
00:32:30,072 --> 00:32:33,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Moving away is just what they want!</font>

438
00:32:34,805 --> 00:32:37,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So I think we need to--</font>

439
00:32:37,371 --> 00:32:40,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't you even think
about trying to catch this person.</font>

440
00:32:43,939 --> 00:32:45,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You have no idea what they're like.</font>

441
00:32:47,072 --> 00:32:48,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wouldn't try to catch them!</font>

442
00:32:49,371 --> 00:32:50,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I see.</i></font>

443
00:32:51,271 --> 00:32:53,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So that's why you want to move out.</font>

444
00:32:53,271 --> 00:32:54,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

445
00:32:54,905 --> 00:32:57,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But we're still minors.</font>

446
00:32:58,271 --> 00:33:01,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So I was wondering
if you could show us a place</font>

447
00:33:01,171 --> 00:33:03,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that would rent even to us.</font>

448
00:33:10,905 --> 00:33:15,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara, you've lost some weight,
haven't you?</font>

449
00:33:16,238 --> 00:33:17,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I have?</font>

450
00:33:18,605 --> 00:33:21,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're working hard at your jobs too,
aren't you?</font>

451
00:33:23,839 --> 00:33:25,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

452
00:33:26,205 --> 00:33:31,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you move again,
it will cost a lot of money.</font>

453
00:33:34,271 --> 00:33:40,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I understand your situation,</font>

454
00:33:40,105 --> 00:33:44,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but maybe you should take this chance
to live separately.</font>

455
00:33:46,505 --> 00:33:49,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you keep living together,</font>

456
00:33:50,738 --> 00:33:53,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you two might suffer</font>

457
00:33:55,005 --> 00:33:57,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">even more harm.</font>

458
00:33:59,839 --> 00:34:01,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you for worrying about us.</font>

459
00:34:03,238 --> 00:34:08,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But...
living apart defeats the whole point.</font>

460
00:34:11,005 --> 00:34:13,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's worth it,
even if it means losing weight.</font>

461
00:34:15,305 --> 00:34:16,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

462
00:34:36,072 --> 00:34:37,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My phone!</font>

463
00:34:39,538 --> 00:34:40,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where is it?</font>

464
00:34:49,238 --> 00:34:50,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's she doing?</font>

465
00:34:55,572 --> 00:34:57,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Take that!</font>

466
00:35:05,271 --> 00:35:06,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao!</font>

467
00:35:19,939 --> 00:35:20,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who is this guy?</font>

468
00:35:21,572 --> 00:35:22,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yu?</font>

469
00:35:24,572 --> 00:35:25,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What on earth are you doing here?</font>

470
00:35:30,472 --> 00:35:32,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">QUIT LIVING TOGETHER AND DUMP NAO,
OR YOU'LL REGRET IT!</font>

471
00:35:35,005 --> 00:35:36,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So you're the one?</font>

472
00:35:37,305 --> 00:35:40,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's all your fault,
two timing her like that.</font>

473
00:35:41,605 --> 00:35:42,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've been making her cry.</font>

474
00:35:43,805 --> 00:35:44,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

475
00:35:44,772 --> 00:35:49,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought that if they broke up,
then you'd stop crying over him.</font>

476
00:35:50,005 --> 00:35:51,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What in the world are you talking about?</font>

477
00:35:51,705 --> 00:35:56,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Isn't this guy your boyfriend?</font>

478
00:35:56,738 --> 00:35:59,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Is that true?</font>

479
00:35:59,972 --> 00:36:01,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you kidding?</font>

480
00:36:04,371 --> 00:36:05,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're so stupid!</font>

481
00:36:12,305 --> 00:36:15,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mami had been acting odd for a while,</font>

482
00:36:15,338 --> 00:36:16,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">so I followed her.</font>

483
00:36:16,905 --> 00:36:19,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She would buy food
and visit this building.</font>

484
00:36:19,705 --> 00:36:23,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You were following me? You're crazy.</font>

485
00:36:23,105 --> 00:36:24,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You were sad because he cheated on you.</font>

486
00:36:24,772 --> 00:36:25,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I couldn't ignore it.</font>

487
00:36:27,271 --> 00:36:29,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So you thought Uehara was my boyfriend?</font>

488
00:36:30,039 --> 00:36:35,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He <i>was your first love, right?</i></font>

489
00:36:35,072 --> 00:36:36,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That was so long ago.</font>

490
00:36:36,405 --> 00:36:40,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's why you blackmailed him?
Wow! You're a real screw up.</font>

491
00:36:41,805 --> 00:36:43,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This pisses me off.</font>

492
00:36:43,438 --> 00:36:46,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">For the longest time,
you've been pissing me off too!</font>

493
00:36:47,705 --> 00:36:49,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">In elementary school,</font>

494
00:36:49,072 --> 00:36:52,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you refused her first true-love chocolates
that she gave you.</font>

495
00:36:54,039 --> 00:36:55,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, Yu!</font>

496
00:36:55,371 --> 00:36:58,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sure you can't understand
my frustration.</font>

497
00:36:59,472 --> 00:37:03,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So basically, her first love was Uehara,</font>

498
00:37:03,405 --> 00:37:06,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and your first love was her.</font>

499
00:37:07,705 --> 00:37:10,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's sure hard to get over
your first love.</font>

500
00:37:13,505 --> 00:37:15,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I really am sorry about this.</font>

501
00:37:15,205 --> 00:37:17,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I did this all on my own.</font>

502
00:37:17,839 --> 00:37:20,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So go ahead and tell the police,
or the school.</font>

503
00:37:21,105 --> 00:37:23,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm ready for whatever happens.</font>

504
00:37:29,538 --> 00:37:30,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Forget it.</font>

505
00:37:34,105 --> 00:37:37,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But if you ever try anything funny again,</font>

506
00:37:38,271 --> 00:37:40,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll make you pay.</font>

507
00:37:40,805 --> 00:37:43,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You sure you want to let him go?</font>

508
00:37:43,638 --> 00:37:46,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-He's broken the law--
-Forget about it.</font>

509
00:37:50,905 --> 00:37:51,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's go, Yu.</font>

510
00:37:56,205 --> 00:37:57,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait!</font>

511
00:38:02,105 --> 00:38:03,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Apologize!</font>

512
00:38:06,572 --> 00:38:08,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Apologize to Uehara.</font>

513
00:38:08,338 --> 00:38:10,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Forget it, Nao.
-I can't!</font>

514
00:38:12,305 --> 00:38:15,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You called him a scumbag.</font>

515
00:38:16,839 --> 00:38:18,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Apologize to him for that!</font>

516
00:38:35,772 --> 00:38:37,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

517
00:38:48,738 --> 00:38:50,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I envy those two.</font>

518
00:38:51,939 --> 00:38:55,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can tell that they're together
because they truly love each other.</font>

519
00:38:57,171 --> 00:38:58,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No wonder I feel this way.</font>

520
00:38:59,438 --> 00:39:01,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought I could share
the happiness he feels</font>

521
00:39:01,338 --> 00:39:03,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">if I am with Uehara.</font>

522
00:39:04,338 --> 00:39:06,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I hurt his girlfriend too.</font>

523
00:39:07,505 --> 00:39:09,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm a terrible person.</font>

524
00:39:09,072 --> 00:39:11,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you're a terrible person,
what does that make me?</font>

525
00:39:11,338 --> 00:39:14,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm the one who tried to blackmail them.</font>

526
00:39:17,305 --> 00:39:18,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Good question.</font>

527
00:39:21,138 --> 00:39:23,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I wish I could have a romance like that.</font>

528
00:39:36,605 --> 00:39:37,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is that the guy?</font>

529
00:39:39,505 --> 00:39:40,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Forget it!</font>

530
00:39:40,939 --> 00:39:42,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-But--
-Just forget about it.</font>

531
00:39:45,271 --> 00:39:48,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want you to dump him.</font>

532
00:39:49,572 --> 00:39:52,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't date guys that cheat.</font>

533
00:39:56,271 --> 00:39:57,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You sure talk big.</font>

534
00:40:01,905 --> 00:40:04,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait up, would you?</font>

535
00:40:08,672 --> 00:40:10,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That settles that.</font>

536
00:40:11,072 --> 00:40:12,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks for helping, Issei.</font>

537
00:40:12,205 --> 00:40:13,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No problem.</font>

538
00:40:13,605 --> 00:40:15,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, thanks for letting me stay here.</font>

539
00:40:16,605 --> 00:40:19,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can come again anytime--</font>

540
00:40:19,205 --> 00:40:20,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't ever come again!</font>

541
00:40:23,338 --> 00:40:24,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Later.</font>

542
00:40:24,738 --> 00:40:26,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah. Bye.</font>

543
00:40:49,271 --> 00:40:50,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're creeping me out again.</font>

544
00:40:53,972 --> 00:40:55,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's just that</font>

545
00:40:55,839 --> 00:40:58,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">we solved the blackmail problem,</font>

546
00:40:58,705 --> 00:41:01,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and Issei and his dad have made up,</font>

547
00:41:01,538 --> 00:41:05,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and Yu's student teaching is over.</font>

548
00:41:13,672 --> 00:41:15,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's finally just us two.</font>

549
00:41:18,672 --> 00:41:20,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara!</font>

550
00:41:30,338 --> 00:41:31,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

551
00:41:31,839 --> 00:41:33,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Where did he go?
<i>-I'm leaving now.</i></font>

552
00:41:34,271 --> 00:41:37,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Hey! Wait a minute!</font>

553
00:41:37,872 --> 00:41:39,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait for me, Uehara!</font>

554
00:41:39,672 --> 00:41:41,238
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait up!</font>

555
00:41:58,371 --> 00:41:59,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">YOSHIKAWA NAO AND UEHARA HISASHI</font>

556
00:41:59,638 --> 00:42:01,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">ARE LIVING TOGETHER!</font>

557
00:42:01,338 --> 00:42:03,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">HOW DID SHE SEDUCE HIM?</font>

558
00:42:13,905 --> 00:42:17,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh, Nao.
-Are you all right?</font>

559
00:42:17,839 --> 00:42:21,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So the blackmailing isn't solved.</font>

560
00:42:21,138 --> 00:42:23,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's happening at school
is a different person.</font>

561
00:42:30,538 --> 00:42:34,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you think it's true that Nao
and Uehara are living together?</font>

562
00:42:34,972 --> 00:42:36,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Quit saying that crap!</font>

563
00:42:37,905 --> 00:42:39,371
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's total bull shit.</font>

564
00:42:56,305 --> 00:42:57,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you going to do about this?</font>

565
00:42:58,271 --> 00:42:59,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">About what?</font>

566
00:42:59,638 --> 00:43:01,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The rumors about living together.</font>

567
00:43:02,105 --> 00:43:02,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, that.</font>

568
00:43:03,039 --> 00:43:05,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're an idiot
if you think you can just ignore it.</font>

569
00:43:05,572 --> 00:43:07,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not ignoring it.</font>

570
00:43:08,338 --> 00:43:11,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm telling you this
because I'm Nao's friend.</font>

571
00:43:11,805 --> 00:43:14,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't care how it affects you.</font>

572
00:43:15,271 --> 00:43:18,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean, you're a guy, after all.</font>

573
00:43:19,905 --> 00:43:21,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But with rumors like that,</font>

574
00:43:21,072 --> 00:43:23,638
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">do you have any idea what happens
to a girl's reputation?</font>

575
00:43:24,772 --> 00:43:26,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yeah, I do.
-No, you don't!</font>

576
00:43:28,672 --> 00:43:31,338
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When all your girl fans
start spouting lies,</font>

577
00:43:31,405 --> 00:43:33,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">it could easily end up hurting Nao!</font>

578
00:43:49,005 --> 00:43:52,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I've called this meeting
about this morning's trouble.</i></font>

579
00:43:52,138 --> 00:43:53,738
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Uehara would never do anything like that.</i></font>

580
00:43:53,805 --> 00:43:56,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>But "Where there's smoke, there's fire."</i></font>

581
00:43:56,939 --> 00:44:00,271
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want you to check the truth behind this,
just to make absolutely certain.</font>

582
00:44:03,105 --> 00:44:05,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? I thought you were at work.</font>

583
00:44:05,638 --> 00:44:08,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm going now.
-Oh, I see.</font>

584
00:44:11,638 --> 00:44:13,538
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Uhm...
-Yes?</font>

585
00:44:15,905 --> 00:44:17,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I need to talk to you.</font>

586
00:44:18,972 --> 00:44:20,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">About those posters?</font>

587
00:44:20,738 --> 00:44:24,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It doesn't bother me at all.
I'm completely used to it.</font>

588
00:44:31,371 --> 00:44:32,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What is it, Uehara?</font>

589
00:44:37,605 --> 00:44:38,438
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

590
00:44:39,738 --> 00:44:40,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

591
00:44:43,505 --> 00:44:46,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I... want to live alone.</font>

592
00:44:52,005 --> 00:44:52,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

593
00:46:16,238 --> 00:46:18,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">THIS IS A FICTIONAL DRAMA.</font>
